- 'top three champions in each performance arena' refers to the top three models for each performance metric based on their average performance values; 
- 'most fervent admirers' refers to the users who most recently accessed these models; 
- 'paid homage to them' refers to accessing the models.

- 'precise model' refers to the model having an average accuracy of more than 0.85; 
- 'frequently accessed' refers to more than 10 accesses since January 1, 2023; 
- 'exceptionally high accuracy' refers to the highest average accuracy among the models that meet the criteria.
